title: Ohio State 34, Indiana 27
text: Activate your digital access. Ohio State 34, Indiana 27 Ohio State's Vonn Bell (11) and Jalin Marshall celebrate after Ohio State defeated Indiana, 34-27, in an NCAA college football game Saturday, Oct. 3, 2015 in Bloomington, Ind. Ohio State won 34-27.
